&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;9 ways to bypass Web Application Firewall：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZGlnaXRhbG11bml0aW9uLm1lLzIwMTgvMDIvc3FsLWluamVjdGlvbi05LXdheXMtYnlwYXNzLXdlYi1hcHBsaWNhdGlvbi1maXJld2FsbC8=&#34;&gt;https://www.digitalmunition.me/2018/02/sql-injection-9-ways-bypass-web-application-firewall/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
