&lt;p&gt;5、ctf4 表的列名：&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL2NoaW5hbG92ZXIuc2luYWFwcC5jb20vU1FMLUdCSy9pbmRleC5waHA/aWQ9JWRmJTI3&#34;&gt;http://chinalover.sinaapp.com/SQL-GBK/index.php?id=�&#39;&lt;/span&gt; and 1=2&lt;br /&gt;
